-- 2010-06-22T04:52:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/gazprom-may-cut-more-gas-supplies-to-belarus-talks-go-on-interfax-says.html

          
          
             OAO Gazprom  said it may further
reduce gas flows to Belarus, after cutting 15 percent of
supplies yesterday, while talks are set to continue at 10 a.m.,
Interfax reported, citing the Russian gas monopoly spokesman,
 Sergei Kupriyanov .  
 Gazprom canâ€™t wait two weeks for Belarus to repay the debt,
Kupiyanov said, the news agency reported.  
